proof_steps: intros A B H H0 H1.

ex_imp_ex.lemma_name:
ex_imp_ex  :
 forall (A:Type)(P Q:A->Prop), (ex P)->(forall x:A, P x -> Q x)->(ex Q).

proof_steps: intros A P Q [y Hy] H.
intros P Q R H1 H2 HP.

le_mult_mult.lemma_name:
le_mult_mult  :
   forall a b c d:nat, a <= c -> b <= d -> a * b <= c * d.

proof_steps: intros a b c d H1 H2.

lt_S.lemma_name: lt_S  : forall n p:nat, n < p -> n < S p.

mult_le_compat_r.lemma_name: mult_le_compat_r  : forall m n p:nat, le n p -> le (n * m) (p * m).

keep_length.lemma_name:
keep_length  :
  forall (n:nat)(v:t A n), length (vector_to_list n v) = n.

wp_o_head_c.lemma_name:
wp_o_head_c  :
 forall l1 l2:list par, wp l1 -> wp l2 -> wp (open :: l1 ++ close :: l2).

wp_o_tail_c.lemma_name:
wp_o_tail_c  :
 forall l1 l2:list par,
   wp l1 -> wp l2 -> wp (l1 ++ open :: l2 ++ close :: nil).

impredicative_le_n.lemma_name: impredicative_le_n  : forall n: nat, impredicative_le n n.

impredicative_sorted_to_sorted.lemma_name:
impredicative_sorted_to_sorted  :
    forall l, impredicative_sorted  l -> sorted  l.

proof_steps: intros x1 x2 l' H1 H2.
intros x1 x2 l' H1 H2.

isorted2.lemma_name:
isorted2  :
    forall (x1 x2:A)(l':list A),
      R x1 x2 ->
      impredicative_sorted  (x2::l') ->
      impredicative_sorted  (x1::x2::l').

proof_steps: intros x1 x2 l' Hrel Hsorted.
